{"tid":19424,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人落唔到手del對話記錄?","createTime":"2016-12-02T18:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T11:00:20.000Z","uid":11548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7736e2366ee283ea3ce2622a5ad38af05a68c55b","tid":19424,"uid":11548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:31:29.000Z","msg":"即使而家比對方block左都好<br />\n純文字都唔夠皮<br />\n間唔中仲開返d voice message出黎聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到播完果刻 理性帶你返到現實果下抽離感...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd4c59bd414ccca98c610cb1745fe600a6ea3b4","tid":19424,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:34:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5857ff2d6d31320cdc0d3f9f2888bc9e0b3365f0","tid":19424,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:34:17.000Z","msg":"舊電話已壞，無back up，唔知好事定壞事<br />\n話咁快就兩年了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604a3e9e43203cdfa4fa0967fcc93799e28c6784","tid":19424,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:35:16.000Z","msg":"自虐狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2459ff38a8dc9d668e2d0dfd82a118a0d490dca0","tid":19424,"uid":36590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:35:39.000Z","msg":"唔捨得del,但有啲舊record壞機無咗"},{"pid":"9533cb82f531ce4bbbfd8122b9ec7d191def47a1","tid":19424,"uid":11548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:37:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>何必呢, 毒品黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n始終唔夠膽del...<br />\n好驚連唯一一個可以聽返佢把聲既途徑都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7ed7ef7249d325e43abfb53e356b10927abbf9","tid":19424,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:48:47.000Z","msg":"愈黎愈多公事對話 唔del得 要留底 可悲"},{"pid":"f45ba55eacdcc14022481acd64aca96bd949f023","tid":19424,"uid":16085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T19:34:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊電話已壞，無back up，唔知好事定壞事<br />\n話咁快就兩年了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣<br />\n<br />\n分開左之後部六s就傻傻地，無啦啦話個whatsapp version太舊要更新；到我想更新個陣，發現Apple id又有問題，因安全因素暫時封左，即係變左冇得更新，用唔到whatsapp<br />\n<br />\n維持左一兩個禮拜，因為公事問題，愈黎愈需要重用whatsapp。結果解決方法就係，用新appleid del whatsapp再重裝，舊record無哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重裝之後我同佢既東西就得番啲群組，有個係我同佢地屋企人，又有個係我爸同佢同我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有少少19999，唔組織咁多了"},{"pid":"ead6b7fc7757c2baf4cc5846a9c84db311a15995","tid":19424,"uid":41388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T19:38:28.000Z","msg":"唔捨得之餘 仲會瘋狂backup對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚有一日冇啦啦死機連d回憶都冇晒"},{"pid":"212dcf08dc10198008fac6ecc9c48bcb0c18ad28","tid":19424,"uid":11548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T03:47:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee426ff157ff62d9b854b11b77c75827fa4ce085","tid":19424,"uid":43647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:01:28.000Z","msg":"個時分手唔開心del左成年record,諗返好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成年嘅回憶"},{"pid":"76d5d6185114c98a6f686b8de50bf5e18423342c","tid":19424,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:06:55.000Z","msg":"唔想del<br />\n但都唔想睇返<img src=\"/assets/faces/no