> <br />\n留低既只有text 同photo images<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢d 紀錄話俾自己聽 人生已經越行越遠 年紀越黎越大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c05a7c178198441334d8a24f7a7d84f05c7993","tid":19424,"uid":20329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"msg 無del, 但都唔會㩒入去睇<br />\n反而d 相唔知點算，次次影相嘅都係我...仲有旅行嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會再做影相嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b734662d3dbc2341efcd3522ff3d61deb8a486d","tid":19424,"uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"自從佢冇再搵我 就冇勇氣睇返昔日既對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5dbcbd89701b331d0389c3668d54b8e439e667","tid":19424,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:49:08.000Z","msg":"前幾日一下del晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n13年到依家 同佢既回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869cfc4e6649dfc0bb6f1c51e5094c77008fc955","tid":19424,"uid":11548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前幾日一下del晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n13年到依家 同佢既回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十三年定一三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee5a338d52c04a6001b07df3c77b33f5530e7fd5","tid":19424,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T17:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前幾日一下del晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 13年到依家 同佢既回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\